rows.label: qst200419_0010
rows.name: Ahahahaha!

rows.label: qst200419_0020
rows.name:
As expected, Vasara. Your
movements are just as they were.

rows.label: qst200419_0030
rows.name:
I take back what I said. You
haven't changed at all.

rows.label: qst200419_0040
rows.name: It's just like that time.

rows.label: qst200419_0050
rows.name:
The time you defied me, betrayed your comrades,
and tried to leave the Bloody Lobster.

rows.label: qst200419_0060
rows.name: Ahahahaha!

rows.label: qst200419_0070
rows.name: ...What's so funny?

rows.label: qst200419_0080
rows.name: What's funny? Isn't it? Isn't this fun?

rows.label: qst200419_0090
rows.name:
To be able to have a death match with
you again, it's the best feeling!

rows.label: qst200419_0100
rows.name: ...I believe I told you.

rows.label: qst200419_0110
rows.name: I have no memory of you.

rows.label: qst200419_0120
rows.name: How cold. Well, I don't mind at all.

rows.label: qst200419_0130
rows.name:
I'm a very kind person, you see. I'll
bury you with my own hands once more.

rows.label: qst200419_0140
rows.name: Just like twenty years ago! Ahahahaha!

rows.label: qst200419_0150
rows.name:
It is useless. In this situation,
you have no chance of victory.

rows.label: qst200419_0160
rows.name:
Hah? What, are you planning
to rely on your friends?

rows.label: qst200419_0170
rows.name: The great Vasara-sama?

rows.label: qst200419_0180
rows.name:
To be sure, I only needed
to assassinate you...

rows.label: qst200419_0190
rows.name:
But with such a large audience,
I can't very well do that.

rows.label: qst200419_0200
rows.name:
Well, either way, I can just
kill them all along with you...

rows.label: qst200419_0210
rows.name: So there's no problem at all.
